<font color=#FFFF00>Apa sebenarnya maksudmu?</font>

285
00:19:44,941 --> 00:19:47,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimanapun, kau harus berbagi...</font>

286
00:19:47,840 --> 00:19:49,880
